flowchart TD
  A[Deploy completed] --> B[Fetch live URLs]
  B --> C[HTTP status check]
  C --> D[Canonical and robots check]
  D --> E[Schema and metadata check]
  E --> F[Tracking hook check]
  F --> G[Sitemap inclusion check]
  G --> H[GSC readiness check]
  H --> I{Critical issue?}
  I -- No --> J[Mark live healthy or live with warnings]
  I -- Yes --> K[Mark rollback recommended]
  K --> L[Prepare rollback point]
  J --> M[Start monitoring window]
